node.text:
It’s #WorldBreastfeedingWeek!
⁣
Breast milk is the ideal first food for a baby 👶. It's safe, clean and contains antibodies which help protect against illnesses.⁣
⁣
✅ Start #breastfeeding 🤱 within 1 hour after birth⁣
✅ Breastfeeding 🤱 exclusively for the first 6 months⁣
✅ Continue breastfeeding 🤱 until the baby 👶 is at least 2 years old

node.text:
As #Angola’s 🇦🇴 rollout of #COVID19 vaccines ramps up, a mall in the nation’s capital has been converted to serve up life-saving vaccines. Paz Flor is one of 21 major vaccination hubs spread across the country’s 18 provinces that bring crucial COVID-19 vaccination services together under one roof.⁣
⁣
Angola has administered more than 1.6 million COVID-19 vaccine doses 💉, with over 1.3 million vaccines received through COVAX .⁣
⁣
#COVAX, the vaccines pillar of the Access to COVID-19 Tools (ACT) Accelerator, is co-led by the WHO, CEPI and @gavialliance – working in partnership with developed and developing country vaccine manufacturers, @UNICEF, @worldbank, and others.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Let’s #ACTogether for #VaccinEquity!⁣⁣⁣
⁣
📸 ©️ WHO / Carlos Cesar
